Package: wcvpmatch
Title: Taxonomic Name Reconciliation Against the WCVP Backbone
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: c(
        person("Paul Efren", "Santos Andrade",
        email = "paulefrens@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Tools for taxonomic name reconciliation against the World
    Checklist of Vascular Plants (WCVP), accessed via
    'rWCVPdata::wcvp_names'. The package standardizes scientific plant
    names and performs exact and fuzzy matching for binomial and trinomial
    names, including infraspecific rank-aware validation. It is designed to
    support reproducible workflows using versioned WCVP snapshots, enabling
    consistent taxonomic processing prior to downstream biodiversity,
    spatial, and trait analyses.
